<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>@ViewData["Title"] - StudentManager</title>

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Quicksand:wght@300;400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://code.ionicframework.com/ionicons/2.0.1/css/ionicons.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" integrity="sha512-9usAa10IRO0HhonpyAIVpjrylPvoDwiPUiKdWk5t3PyolY1cOd4DSE0Ga+ri4AuTroPR5aQvXU9xC6qOPnzFeg==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/lib/admin-lte/css/adminlte.css">

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/site.css" asp-append-version="true" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/StudentManager.styles.css" asp-append-version="true" />
</head>

<body>
    <div class="auth-fluid">
        <div class="auth-fluid-right">
            <div class="auth-user-testimonial">
                <h3 class="mb-3 text-white">Very elegant &amp; impressive!</h3>
                <p class="lead fw-normal">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-quote-left"></i>
                    Nulla quis magna non velit molestie ornare. Cras non purus nec libero mollis interdum. Suspendisse fermentum justo sed odio eleifend, vel iaculis tortor aliquet. Pellentesque condimentum ipsum eget lectus mollis sodales. Nam iaculis vestibulum nulla id vehicula. Integer vitae efficitur ligula. Curabitur tellus libero, feugiat ac quam id, iaculis faucibus risus. Maecenas eleifend mollis fermentum.
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-quote-right"></i>
                </p>
                <h5 class="text-white">
                    
                </h5>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="auth-fluid-form-box">
            <div class="align-items-center d-flex h-100">
                @RenderBody()
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="~/lib/jquery/dist/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="~/lib/bootstrap/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="~/lib/admin-lte/js/adminlte.js"></script>

    <script src="~/js/site.js" asp-append-version="true"></script>
    @await RenderSectionAsync("Scripts", required: false)
</body>
</html>
